	measure 'Sublot Hedges Positions Title' = ```
			
			VAR maxPerd =
			    MAX ( 'Securities Sublot Fact'[As of Date] )
			VAR repCur =
			    SELECTEDVALUE ( 'Reporting Currency'[Rep In Currency] )
			VAR title =
			    "Sublot Hedges Positions, " & repCur & ", "
			        & SELECTEDVALUE ( Framework[Framework Display] ) & ", "
			        & FORMAT ( maxPerd, "dd-Mmm-yy" )
			RETURN
			    title
			
			```
		lineageTag: 172331a2-2852-4516-99be-af1a9aa55489

